{"tid":1435431,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"［大台唔係到，集思廣益］勇武暫停到幾時","createTime":"2019-08-09T04:57:13.000Z","updateTime":"2019-08-09T05:05:03.000Z","uid":240372,"like":1,"dislike":1,"uniUserReply":2,"replies":[{"pid":"5c8b38930b20f6e5617e826c558632f8f45a7704","tid":1435431,"uid":240372,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-09T04:57:13.000Z","msg":"大家都知勇武，和理非兩者相輔相成，缺一不可，<br />\n只要係可以達到目的，我地就應該做應該做的事。<br />\n<br />\n5/8林鄭話示威者係革命分子，企圖分化市民大眾與示威者。其後舉行既4點鐘記者會就不停透過大氣電波洗市民腦。<br />\n幸好，不割席鐵律縱然受到考驗，但係大家仍算能堅守，勇武亦明顯能保持理性，可以做到收放自如。俾d掌聲佢地。<br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/dance2.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/dance2.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/dance2.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/dance2.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n但係而家勇武就收左啦，但係幾時要放呢？太長時間唔放會唔會熄左團火，<span style=\"color: red;\">重蹈雨傘覆轍？</span><br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n仲有想問，民陣去左邊<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n2014年：唔好搞金紫荊，唔好搞升旗。2019年：唔好搞不合作，唔好圍警署<br />\n<a href=\"https://lih.kg/1435288\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://lih.kg/1435288</a><br />\n- 分享自 LIHKG 討論區"},{"pid":"f6305ae6bc5df1d6f1cbdd158e4a787c9bb8f600","tid":1435431,"uid":240372,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-09T05:00:37.000Z","msg":"推"},{"pid":"9b176327ae5d9ed515c21de566865fe4ca01bff4","tid":1435431,"uid":276219,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-09T05:05:03.000Z","msg":"你叫民間記招宣佈升級死線 咪即係俾位政府入佢哋煽動 推佢哋去送死?<br />\n而家叫抖一抖 回下氣 唔係全停呀"}]}